Their union is the coemergent vajra mind.
Glorious protectors of beings, to you we give praise.

Flowing robes and dangling ornaments—memory, eloquence, and the major and minor marks;
The five pleasures displayed—the untainted aggregates;
The sublime and precious royal attributes—the seven noble riches,
We offer with the auspicious articles, the eight perfect freedoms.

